Mr. Kraus: First off, [color=firebrick]lying[/color] is not just [color=firebrick]lying[/color]. It's a skill to develop.
Mr. Kraus: Not every [color=firebrick]lie[/color] is worth telling, and sometimes the truth is better.
Mr. Kraus: It all depends on what faction you're trying to appeal to.

do player_data.wait_for_article_choice_click()
Mr. Kraus: For now, click on one of these choices, just like I taught you the other week.
Mr. Kraus: Good.
Mr. Kraus: Now, you may not notice anything different about this choice yet.
Mr. Kraus: If a choice has a [color=firebrick]lying[/color] option, it'll be labeled as such when you scroll over it.

