Mr. Kraus: Try selecting a lie with your scroll wheel and left click.
Mr. Kraus: Good job, kid.
Mr. Kraus: Now if you look at a choice, and it shows up in red, that means that one's a [color=firebrick]lie[/color].
Mr. Kraus: Just[speed=0.35]...[speed=1] Be careful with the [color=firebrick]lies[/color].
Mr. Kraus: [color=firebrick]Lies[/color] can be a good tool, but too many of them can dig you into a hole you can't get out of easily.
Mr. Kraus: Finish this article up, then click submit like usual.
Mr. Kraus: And don't worry, it's all for testing, so no bunnies are getting smuggled.
